Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
## Lists, Rows, and Columns

`Row` places expressions from the list in a row. Any strings are converted to normal text by default.

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
## Lists, Rows, and Columns

`Row` places expressions from the list in a row. Any strings are converted to normal text by default.

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Row[{1, "->", 2}]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
(*GB[*){{1(*|*),(*|*)"->"(*|*),(*|*)2}}(*]GB*)

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
Any expressions are valid.

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Any expressions are valid.

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Column[{Red, Blue}]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
(*GB[*){{(*VB[*)(RGBColor[1, 0, 0])(*,*)(*"1:eJxTTMoPSmNkYGAoZgESHvk5KRCeGJAIcndyzs/JLwouTyxJzghJzS3ISSxJTWMGyXMgyRcxgMEHeyiDgQHOAAALpBNd"*)(*]VB*)}(*||*),(*||*){(*VB[*)(RGBColor[0, 0, 1])(*,*)(*"1:eJxTTMoPSmNkYGAoZgESHvk5KRCeGJAIcndyzs/JLwouTyxJzghJzS3ISSxJTWMGyXMgyRcxQAE644M9APZHE10="*)(*]VB*)}}(*]GB*)

