.md
`Grid` is a low-level primitive to construct tables

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
`Grid` is a low-level primitive to construct tables

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Grid @ Table[KroneckerDelta[i,j], {i,3}, {j,3}]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
(*GB[*){{1(*|*),(*|*)0(*|*),(*|*)0}(*||*),(*||*){0(*|*),(*|*)1(*|*),(*|*)0}(*||*),(*||*){0(*|*),(*|*)0(*|*),(*|*)1}}(*]GB*)

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
Grids can be stylized using `Item` (accepts the same options as `Style`).

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Grids can be stylized using `Item` (accepts the same options as `Style`).

